**Story**

Once upn a time  in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon tree, which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest, there lived a Crocodile and his wife. One day, the crocodile came to the bank of river and rested under the tree. The kindhearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits , as he loved them. As days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became god friends.
